  "detailed_description": "<strong>Idle Tower Defense is a stress relieving idle game. If you're tired of operating all the time and hate that you can't always randomize the item you want. Then this is the game for you. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/a5ece6960a041dca48ad9f48c3fd0869.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2><strong>Start with a simple defense tower,  choose from a variety of modules, and create unique builds. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/08de38f20bf1028dd3997f844d99a22c.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dozens of modules</h2><strong>Beat waves to gain points, use points to unlock modules. Simple and straight, no randomization. Unlock whichever you like! </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=378 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/edefaee1ab0fc964b3bfa44d68d01e10.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Idle</h2><strong>Automatically kill enemies and get their gold. Use gold to upgrade modules. Normal weapons will also change.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/5515de3d54c4cb42fa356e0b1885ffa2.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose power, try again</h2><strong>Choose to evolve, gain powerful abilities, and start over in an exclusive form. Stronger builds, faster kills, and a more enjoyable experience!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/014353a83772d647d46596cac4c129f8.poster.avif?t=1763523673\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/014353a83772d647d46596cac4c129f8.webm?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054090/extras/014353a83772d647d46596cac4c129f8.mp4?t=1763523673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
